---
import Title from "../components/Title.astro";
import Text from "../components/Text.astro";
---

<section class="bg-white py-24">
  <div
    class="max-w-screen-2xl w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-12 flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center"
  >
    <Title size="XXL" tag="h2" className="text-center pb-2">
      Pricing Tailored to Your Needs
    </Title>

    <Text size="XL" className="max-w-4xl text-gray-200 text-center pb-4">
      At Progressively, we understand the frustration of unpredictable
      pay-as-you-go pricing. That's why we've created a straightforward pricing
      model designed to make you feel secure, ensuring you only pay for what you
      need. <strong class="font-bold">And it starts at 1 euro</strong>.
    </Text>

    <div class="border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8 max-w-sm">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-xl">The only plan</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xs text-gray-700 text-sm leading-6">
        For anybody that want to improve their product building & delivery
        processes
      </p>

      <div class="py-4 flex flex-row items-center">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-end gap-4">
          <p class="text-black text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold shrink-0">
            1â‚¬
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 shrink-0 text-lg">for</p>
          <p class="text-black text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold shrink-0">
            500
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 shrink-0 text-lg">events*</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-500 shrink-0 text-xs">
        * An event corresponds to 1 flag eval. or 1 analytics hit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
